  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add scallions and ginger, sauté for about 3 minutes until softened.",
    "Stir in garlic, honey/molasses, soy sauce, white wine/beer (if using), lemon juice. Simmer for another minute to reduce the mixture.",
    "Add diced carrots and broccoli florets. Stir occasionally until vegetables are tender-crisp.",
    "If desired, top with pepperoni slices before serving to add a bit of texture and flavor."
